flowchart LR
  A[Agent Client] --> G[Context Gateway (MCP Proxy)]
  G -->|call tool| T[External Tool (e.g., Playwright, GitHub)]
  T -->|raw output| G
  G -->|store raw| B[(Blob/Object Store)]
  G -->|compressed summary + handles| A
  A -->|if needed: drill-down| G
  G -->|fetch slice by handle| B
  G -->|focused snippet| A
